FBIS4-55130 "dreeu090__a94041" FBIS-EEU-94-090-A Daily Report 6 May 1994 ANNEX Slovakia Foreign Ministry Welcomes Israel-PLO Accord Foreign Ministry Welcomes Israel-PLO Accord AU0605163494 Prague CTK in English 1355 GMT 6 May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU0605163494 Prague CTK English BFN [Text] Bratislava, May 6 (CTK) -- The Slovak Foreign Ministry has welcomed the self-rule accord concluded between Israel and Palestine Liberation Organization (PLO), the ministerial press office told CTK today. The accord is an important moment in fulfilling the principles of the Israeli-Palestine agreement which were signed last September in Washington and an important watershed on the way to the definitive settlement of the Arab-Israeli conflict, the ministry stated.
